\begin_inset Formula $x\in\Omega\backslash\left\{ x^{*}\right\} $
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\lVert x-x^{*}\rVert<\varepsilon$
\end_inset

.
 A point 
\begin_inset Formula $x^{*}\in\Omega$
\end_inset

